#. Body copy for the mobile web app (PWA) card on the download page. Preserve {product_name} exactly; mention that it installs like a Progressive Web App. Preserve placeholders exactly.
#: fluxer_marketing/generated:platform_support.mobile.web_app.body
msgctxt "platform_support.mobile.web_app.body"
msgid ""
"{product_name} runs in any mobile browser and installs to your home screen like a Progressive Web App. It is the most complete way to use {product_name} on a phone today."
msgstr ""
"{product_name} 可在任何行動瀏覽器中運作，並可像漸進式網頁應用程式 (PWA) 一樣安裝到您的主畫面上。這是目前在手機上使用 {product_name} 的最完整方式。"

